{"tid":1533052,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"特首辦回覆證實特首上周有出席商界活動 與會者亦應知悉是以不引述出席者言論的，不會評論特首在活動的談話內容","createTime":"2019-09-02T16:05:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T16:12:29.000Z","uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"edf478011848d70ae1f64d0f026e8f25c47488e0","tid":1533052,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:05:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1478457-20190902.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1478457-20190902.htm&d=7ie9SmB3qTQYrTFhvLfIgQEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=37d9463e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1478457-20190902.htm&h=4c8af83d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1478457-20190902.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n路透社在報道中說，取得行政長官林鄭月娥，與商界閉門會議的一段錄音，林鄭月娥在會議中說作為行政長官，引發一場政治危機，造成「不能原諒的破壞」，如果有選擇，她第一項會做的是辭職並道歉。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥說，只是有非常有限的空間，去解決這次修例事件，因為事件已升級成與國家主權及國家安全有關，中央政府了解到如果解放軍到港平息示威活動，會對中國的國際聲譽造成影響，並付出極大代價，中央重視國際社會的評論。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又說，對不能減少前線警務人員的壓力、不能提供方法，平息和平示威者的憤怒，感到極大沮喪和悲哀。<br />\n<br />\n報道說，有3名出席會面的人士，證實林鄭月娥曾說出有關說話。<br />\n<br />\n特首辦回覆查詢時說，行政長官上星期，出席兩項有商界人士參與的活動，兩項活動均有向與會者表明、與會者亦應知悉是以不引述出席者言論的原則進行，因此不會評論行政長官在活動的談話內容。"},{"pid":"484fd7a244fd33ab9c881ea0a4ba4caffffd2450","tid":1533052,"uid":132497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:05:56.000Z","msg":"希望有人幫手統籌<br />\n<br />\n[創舉] 10月1日，香港人要搞個健力士世界紀錄<br />\n<br />\n如果個日全香港人舉唔同國家既國旗，唯獨是無中共垃圾旗，搞個健力士世界紀錄，有無得諗<br />\n<br />\n香港人要入健力士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n落佢鬼國面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[Record breaking] Oct 1, HongKongers need to break a Guiness World Record<br />\n<br />\nIf all the HongKongers carry different countries national flags, except the one of CCP, and break a Guiness World Record, sound good?<br />\n<br />\nHongKongers need to break a Guiness World Record<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nLose ChiNazi&rsquo;s face<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532234\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532234</a>"},{"pid":"39c10bc342f764c50ee89bfd887649c62d415c34","tid":1533052,"uid":193346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:07:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而家先黎示弱呀屌你老母？之前唔係好撚串既咩？家下打死人就諗住一硬一軟想我地收皮？<br />\n我屌你老母啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"692644531e4c1f034d4825c84fb8d42663b0905f","tid":1533052,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:10:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38708cec940f24651d577901ec4d4566dacdfa78","tid":1533052,"uid":287449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:12:29.000Z","msg":"再次特首講野唔代表政府，咁邊個講野先代表到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />借位宣傳<br />\n侵侵同d外國人都冇加你fb同ig，點知你想要咩啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好再係facebook同ig自己圍爐打飛機啦，一齊黎開始國際戰線！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個tweet幾秒鐘，一蚊都唔洗，又唔洗綁電話，安全又快捷，快d一齊轉用twitter啦<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">twitter文宣共識TG</span>： </span></strong><a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=7ie9SmB3qTQYrTFhvLfIgQEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=a4e42ebd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n內有twitter詳細教學，開個account唔洗3分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n英文唔好驚比人笑？唔洗驚，國際文宣谷幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/